nderebilece\'f0i yap\'fds\'fdyla birlikte yarat\'fdlm\'fd\'fet\'fdr.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs22\up6\lang1024\langfe1024\langnp1055\insrsid6304561\charrsid4653801 22}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
