\f8\fs20\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1033\langfenp1055 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs22\lang1024\langfe1024\langnp1055\insrsid6304561\charrsid4653801 Bitkilerin fotosentez i\'feleminde kullanacaklar\'fd tek enerji kayna\'f0\'fd
